origin.latoorigins.axolotl.name: Axolotl
origin.latoorigins.astronos.name: Astronos
origin.latoorigins.astronos.description: Peaceful creatures of the skies. These creatures have fragile health, because they don't fight.
origin.latoorigins.cobblestonian.name: Cobblestonian

origin.latoorigins.dimensional_being.des: No information gathered on this entity. . .
origin.latoorigins.goatlin.name: Goatlin
origin.latoorigins.goatlin.description: You are a goatlin, leaping from peak to peak with incredible agility, and jump height.
origin.latoorigins.god.name: God
origin.latoorigins.god.description: God is the creator of all beings.
origin.latoorigins.iron_golem.name: Iron Golem
origin.latoorigins.iron_golem.descriptio: Iron golem are built to protect others.
origin.latoorigins.lato.name: Lato
origin.latoorigins.lato.description: Latos banished Daltogs to the nether long ago, and now about all of the Latos are gone.

origin.latoorigins.lava_sharkian.descrip: Lava sharkians are the ruler of the lava oceans.

origin.latoorigins.sharkian.description: Sharkians are the ruler of the oceans, and they would rule the land too, if they could breathe on it.

origin.latoorigins.tauros.description: Tauros are the guardians of the plains, calmly grazing the grass.

origin.latoorigins.trashling.description: Trashlings did not have much to eat, and as they evolved, the began learning how to eat more things. Now they can eat almost anything.
origin.latoorigins.warden.name: 地城守護者
origin.latoorigins.warden.description: Wardens are cave monsters, always lurking in the darkness.
power.latoorigins.adaptive.name: Adaptive
power.latoorigins.adaptive.description: You can adapt to dimensions with ease.
power.latoorigins.arcane_skin.name: Arcane Skin
power.latoorigins.arcane_skin.descriptio: An arcane skin, which is a different color from most.
power.latoorigins.bite_sized.name: Bite Sized
power.latoorigins.blindness.name: Blindness
power.latoorigins.blindness.description: You are blind when you don't have enough hunger for your eyes.
power.latoorigins.bombing.name: Bombing
power.latoorigins.bombing.description: You are able to go at incredible speeds when you are in homing missile mode.

power.latoorigins.built_up_dash.descript: Charge in any direction at high speeds, but you have to build up speed first.
Your body is made out of clouds, allowing you to become water vapor, thus avoiding every attack, except starvation.
power.latoorigins.cloud_skin.name: Cloud Skin
power.latoorigins.cloud_skin.description: Your skin is of clouds, causing it to be transparent.
power.latoorigins.cobblestone_skin.name: Cobblestone Skin
power.latoorigins.cobblestone_skin.descr: Skin made out of cobblestone, causing you to be tougher than most.
power.latoorigins.composter.name: Composter
power.latoorigins.composter.description: When eating, you have a chance to create bonemeal.
power.latoorigins.delicious_kelp.name: Delicious Kelp
power.latoorigins.delicious_kelp.descrip: Kelp tastes extra delicious to you.

power.latoorigins.finned.name: Finned
power.latoorigins.finned.description: You can only inch towards your target on land.
power.latoorigins.gnashing_teeth.name: Gnashing Teeth
power.latoorigins.gnashing_teeth.descrip: Teeth that allow for terrifying attack damage whilst submerged in water.
power.latoorigins.goat_dash.name: Goat Dash
power.latoorigins.goat_dash.description: Legs that allow for a short burst of speed.
power.latoorigins.grass_graze.name: Grass Graze
power.latoorigins.grass_graze.descriptio: You can eat grass to gain some food.
power.latoorigins.habitat_advantage.name: Habitat Advantage
power.latoorigins.habitat_advantage.desc: You feel more at home in the plains.
power.latoorigins.heated_skin.name: Heated Skin
power.latoorigins.heated_skin.descriptio: A heated skin allows for cuts to be quickly healed.

power.latoorigins.hoofed.description: Your legs are shaped different causing you to move faster, but swim slower.

power.latoorigins.iron_body.description: A body made out of iron provides more health, but costs speed and size.
power.latoorigins.iron_diet.name: Iron Diet

power.latoorigins.iron_knowledge.name: Iron Knowledge
power.latoorigins.lato_blooded.name: Lato Blooded
power.latoorigins.lato_blooded.descripti: Lato's blood can work out metallic poisoning.
power.latoorigins.lava_finned.name: Finned
power.latoorigins.lava_finned.descriptio: You can only inch towards your target on land.
power.latoorigins.lava_swimming.name: Lava Swimming
power.latoorigins.lava_swimming_speed.de: Your body is built to go faster in lava.
power.latoorigins.lava_torpedo.name: Lava Torpedo
power.latoorigins.lava_torpedo.descripti: Tear through lava at high speeds.
power.latoorigins.lightweight.name: Lightweight
power.latoorigins.lightweight.descriptio: A featherweighted body allows for falling to the ground without taking damage.
power.latoorigins.long_arms.name: Long Arms
power.latoorigins.long_arms.description: Longer arms allows for you to have further attack and mining reach.
power.latoorigins.metal_stomach.name: Metal Stomach
power.latoorigins.metal_stomach.descript: Due to eating so many foods, your not able to be poisoned, or get sick.
power.latoorigins.mist_arms.name: Mist Arms
power.latoorigins.mist_arms.description: Arms that can reach terrifying distances.
power.latoorigins.mist_body.name: Mist Body
power.latoorigins.mist_body.description: Your body is made out of mist, causing it to be much weaker.
power.latoorigins.mist_skin.name: Mist Skin
power.latoorigins.mist_skin.description: Misty skin of an inter-dimensional being.
power.latoorigins.monstrous_body.name: Monstrous Body
power.latoorigins.monstrous_body.descrip: A body that allows further reach, stronger attacks, more health, but at the cost of speed, and a larger body.
power.latoorigins.movement_reduction.des: Due to being made up of cobblestone, your body is slower.
power.latoorigins.native_resources.name: Native Resources
power.latoorigins.native_resources.descr: Slightly increased damage using netherite or gold, and allows netherrack to be used as cobblestone.
power.latoorigins.natural_regeneration.d: Natural regeneration passively regenerates your health.
power.latoorigins.need_for_skylight.name: Need for Skylight
power.latoorigins.need_for_skylight.desc: You need skylight to stay in tip-top shape.
power.latoorigins.no_shield.name: Phasing Hands
power.latoorigins.no_shield.description: Shields fall right through your hands, rendering them useless.
power.latoorigins.nuke.name: Nuke
power.latoorigins.nuke.description: Your body was built in a way that allows itself to detonate.
power.latoorigins.neighbors.name: Neighbors
power.latoorigins.neighbors.description: You are familiar with mobs of the nether.
power.latoorigins.old_friends.name: Old Friends
power.latoorigins.old_friends.descriptio: You have known the ruler of the end for a long time.
power.latoorigins.perfect_vision.name: Perfect Vision
power.latoorigins.perfect_vision.descrip: Carefully constructed eyes that allow for perfect vision, they also are toggleable.
power.latoorigins.petrification.name: Petrification
power.latoorigins.petrification.descript: You become immobile, but you take less damage, and are invincible to some things.
power.latoorigins.pickaxeable.name: Pickaxeable

power.latoorigins.radioactive.name: Radioactive

power.latoorigins.rage.name: Rage
power.latoorigins.rage.description: Rage gives strength for a short period of time, but costs health.
power.latoorigins.regenerate.name: Regenerate
power.latoorigins.rideable_creature.name: Rideable
power.latoorigins.rideable_creature.desc: You are able to be ridden.
power.latoorigins.rocky_eater.name: Rocky Eater
power.latoorigins.rocky_eater.descriptio: You can eat ore, and rocks.
power.latoorigins.seven_lives.name: Seven Lives
power.latoorigins.seven_lives.descriptio: Your body causes you to have only seven hearts.
power.latoorigins.sky_swimming.name: Sky Swimming
power.latoorigins.sky_swimming.descripti: You can float through the sky.
power.latoorigins.small_appetite.name: Small Appetite
power.latoorigins.small_appetite.descrip: You are less hungry, and need to eat less.
power.latoorigins.translucent_body.name: Translucent Body

power.latoorigins.trashlike_appetite.des: You are able to eat just about everything.
power.latoorigins.tough_hide.name: Tough Hide
power.latoorigins.tough_hide.description: Tougher hide allows you to take more hits.
power.latoorigins.underwater_allies.name: Underwater Allies
power.latoorigins.underwater_allies.desc: You are familiar with underwater creatures.
power.latoorigins.underwater_home.name: Underwater Home
power.latoorigins.unhealthy_food.name: Unhealthy Food
power.latoorigins.unhealthy_food.descrip: Because of an unhealthy diet, you are weaker, slower, and have less health.
power.latoorigins.village_spawn.name: Village Life
power.latoorigins.warp.name: Warp
power.latoorigins.water_torpedo.name: Water Torpedo
power.latoorigins.water_torpedo.descript: Blaze through water at high speeds.
power.latoorigins.water_vision.name: Water Vision
power.latoorigins.water_vision.descripti: You can see much more clearly in water than others.
power.latoorigins.water_vulnerability.de: Your blood boils in water, causing you to take damage after prolonged exposure to it.
power.latoorigins.water_walk.name: Water Walking
power.latoorigins.water_walk.description: Walk on water, just like Jesus.
power.latoorigins.webbed_feet.name: Webbed Feet
power.latoorigins.webbed_feet.descriptio: Your feet are webbed, causing you to move slower on land.
